        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Public Service Pays Off Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to incrementally cancel a percentage of the obligation to repay the balance on eligible Federal Direct Loans for a borrower who, while employed in public service,&nbsp;makes qualifying payments for 2, 4, 6, 8, and 10 years.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
